@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_gtkize(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = wp.cos(wp.exp(wp.sin(v1 + 0.50)))
    v2 = (wp.cos((tmp + 0.81 * v2 + 0.49)) / (wp.abs(tmp + 0.46) * (v1 + 0.73 / v0 + 0.16)))
    v0 = wp.cos((tmp + 0.46))
    tmp = 0.83
    v1 = wp.sin(wp.exp((v0 + 0.32 - v2 + 0.39)))
    v2 = (wp.exp(wp.sin(v2 + 0.82)) + (wp.exp(tmp + 0.32) + 0.66))
    tmp = v2
    v0 = wp.sin(0.30)
    data[tid] = v0
